id: pm-p37b
title: Add performance / startup-latency section to ARCHITECTURE.md
description: "ARCHITECTURE.md has no section on performance characteristics or startup latency. Sessions 2026-05-27 and 2026-05-31 delivered major perf improvements (front-matter cache body-split, drift-scan verification cache, non-blocking background semantic refresh, per-command code-splitting via detached handlers). Agents and contributors have no documented model of expected performance, what the remaining bottleneck is (~90ms from ESM module resolution), or how to profile startup cost."
type: Chore
